    • i0

      public int i0
      The numeric representation of the enumeration value as a zero based index.

      This number is the value of an actual attribute of this type and which can be retrieved from an object of type Attribute through its field Attribute.n, e.g. by a template expression like <frame.attribMap.myParticularAttributeName.n>.
